resources.string: You can optimize the performance of single barcode reading by selecting single barcode template.
You can simply optimize the barcode reading speed by selecting speed first template. You can still add your personalized settings to further improve the performance.
You can simply optimize the barcode read rate by selecting read rate first template. You can still add your personalized settings to further improve the performance.
In addition to the general accuracy settings, you can add your personalized configurations to further improve the accuracy.
